label: Very Low
comment: The performance of processes using the asset is not affected if this control is used.

label: Low
comment: The performance of processes using the asset is slightly degraded if this control is used.

label: Medium
comment: The performance of processes using the asset is somewhat degraded if this control is used.

label: High
comment: The performance of processes using the asset is substantially degraded if this control is used.

label: Very High
comment: The performance of processes using the asset is crippled if this control is used.
